The song "Shifting Shapes, Steadfast Heart" takes place during the movie Encanto, after the realization that the family's magic is in danger. Camilo, who has been struggling to understand himself, expresses his fear of losing his identity and searches for where he stands in a world of shifting colors. Mirabel reassures Camilo that his true gift lies in bringing laughter and light to the family. Together, they embark on a journey of self-discovery, embracing their uniqueness and finding strength in unity. The family realizes that their power comes from their bonds and love for each other. They pledge to stand together, face the challenges, and keep the magic alive in their hearts. Camilo, no longer hiding behind different faces, embraces his true essence and vows to sustain the magic with his family.
